"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#brackets\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">[ (en-US)</a> <a href=\"#line-names\">&lt;line-names&gt;</a> <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#single_bar\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">| (en-US)</a> <a href=\"#name-repeat\">&lt;name-repeat&gt;</a> <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#brackets\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">] (en-US)</a><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#plus\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">+ (en-US)</a></code></p><p style=\"font-family:Open Sans,Arial,sans-serif; margin: 10px 0 0 0;\">where <br><code style=\"font-family:Consolas,Monaco,&quot;Andale Mono&quot;,monospace;\"><span id=\"line-names\">&lt;line-names&gt;</span> = '<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#brackets\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">[ (en-US)</a>' <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/custom-ident\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;custom-ident&gt; (en-US)</a><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#asterisk\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">* (en-US)</a> '<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#brackets\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">] (en-US)</a>'<br><span id=\"track-size\">&lt;track-size&gt;</span> = <a href=\"#track-breadth\">&lt;track-breadth&gt;</a> <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#single_bar\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">| (en-US)</a> minmax( <a href=\"#inflexible-breadth\">&lt;inflexible-breadth&gt;</a> , <a href=\"#track-breadth\">&lt;track-breadth&gt;</a> ) <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#single_bar\"